name: Gunpowder

reviews.review_text: Found a recommendation online for Gunpowder and it did not disappoint! The staff invited us in even though they weren’t open yet. The beers were delicious and the cocktails are worth trying a few…highly recommend the Tamarind Spicy Margarita. The portions are good size and so so tasty. Honestly the food was so delicious I will be coming back as soon as I can. Can’t recommend it enough and the staff are so friendly and took time to explain the menu to us.

Once you have tasted above average food here ,that becomes your yardstick ...  thats why ,was a wee bit disappointed at the slipping down on those authentic flavors and missing out longingly on some of the breakfast items which were available earlier ... for someone who knows authentic flavors , this can be a little let down. The inhouse beers were nice ,staff attentive but wish it was more ambient according to how things are priced there.
Best food with good service. Love the host.. She was best (Thresa) was her name if I'm not wrong.. Enjoyed the ambiance too

description:
### Gunpowder: A Culinary Gem in Goa

Nestled in the charming locale of Assonora, Goa, **Gunpowder** boasts an impressive **4.5-star rating** after receiving feedback from **5,278 patrons**. The restaurant is frequently noted for its exceptional **cocktails** (206 mentions), traditional **Goan** cuisine (26 mentions), and standout dishes such as **pork ribs** (19 mentions) and **prawn curry** (13 mentions). These highlights suggest a vibrant concoction of flavors that defines the culinary experience at Gunpowder.

### Ambiance & Design

As you step into Gunpowder, you are greeted by an inviting ambiance filled with warmth and rustic charm. The restaurant's design, illustrated in the stunning photos, features well-placed lighting that creates a cozy, relaxed environment—ideal for both casual dinners and special occasions. The decor is a tasteful blend of traditional elements with a modern twist, underscoring Goa’s rich heritage. Reviewers have mentioned enjoying the ambiance, particularly noting the efforts of staff like Thresa, whose hospitality made their experience memorable.

### Menu & Culinary Experience

Gunpowder excels in delivering a distinctive culinary adventure, with a menu that captures the essence of Goan flavors. Signature dishes such as the **pork ribs** are praised for their tender texture and flavorful marinades, while the **prawn curry** stands out with its rich spices and freshness. Reviewers have highly recommended the **Tamarind Spicy Margarita**, declaring it a must-try cocktail that pairs beautifully with the meal. Portions appear generous, ensuring that each bite is savored. While some guests have expressed a desire for more authentic flavor profiles reminiscent of earlier visits, many still find the offerings to be delightful and satisfying.

### Customer Experience & Service

Service at Gunpowder is frequently highlighted for its attentiveness and staff friendliness. Customers appreciate that the staff take the time to explain the menu, enhancing the overall dining experience. A notable sentiment from reviewers indicates that the team’s welcoming nature significantly contributes to the feel-good atmosphere of the restaurant. However, one guest did suggest that the ambiance could better align with price points, hinting at a need for a bit more finesse in the overall setting.

### Popularity & Reviews

With a steady stream of positive feedback and social media buzz, Gunpowder has built a reputation as a must-visit dining spot in Goa. Customers have expressed their desires to return, citing the food and cocktails as primary reasons. Although a few reviews mentioned some inconsistency in flavor over time, the majority celebrate the quality and creativity of the dishes served. The restaurant’s popularity is evident in its vibrant crowd, even during off-peak hours.

### Visual Highlights

The accompanying photographs truly encapsulate the essence of Gunpowder. From the beautifully plated dishes that showcase the culinary artistry to the inviting interior that seduces the eye, each image resonates with the lively spirit of the restaurant. One particular image stands out, showcasing the intimate dining space filled with patrons enjoying their meals, which effectively communicates the restaurant’s vibrant atmosphere.

In conclusion, **Gunpowder** in Assonora delivers a delightful dining experience that marries Goa's culinary heritage with a modern twist. Whether you're sipping on expertly crafted cocktails or indulging in authentic dishes, visitors can expect a memorable meal supported by friendly service and a warm, inviting ambiance. This culinary gem is poised to become a staple for both locals and travelers alike.
